238
00:16:34,650 --> 00:16:36,280
Tak semudah itu.

239
00:16:36,690 --> 00:16:37,960
Kau ambil ini.

240
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:39,400
Setelah masuk ke Wilayah Bintang,

241
00:16:39,410 --> 00:16:41,080
cobalah untuk mengoleskan darah yang tersisa,

242
00:16:41,090 --> 00:16:42,760
di dahi Three Thousand Burning Flame.

243
00:16:43,410 --> 00:16:46,320
Kemudian segel naga yang tersembunyi di dalamnya akan teraktifkan.

244
00:16:46,970 --> 00:16:47,720
Tapi,

245
00:16:47,850 --> 00:16:49,120
aku sarankan agar kau menunggu,

246
00:16:49,130 --> 00:16:50,720
sampai bocah itu kehabisan tenaga sebelum bertindak.

247
00:16:50,890 --> 00:16:52,160
Dengan begitu, peluang suksesnya,

248
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:52,920
akan jauh lebih besar.

249
00:16:53,450 --> 00:16:54,800
Kalau gagal bagaimana?

250
00:16:55,570 --> 00:16:56,640
Itu...

251
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,520
Segel naga itu bersifat relatif.

252
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,720
Jika kau gagal,

253
00:17:01,810 --> 00:17:05,120
ada kemungkinan,

254
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:07,520
dia yang akan mengontrolmu.

255
00:17:09,970 --> 00:17:11,600
Ini...

256
00:17:11,610 --> 00:17:13,290
Konsekuensi kegagalan ini,

257
00:17:13,370 --> 00:17:14,960
Xiao Yan, kau tidak bisa mengambil risiko ini!

258
00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:17,680
Kalau tidak seperti ini,

259
00:17:17,690 --> 00:17:20,400
pasti tidak bisa menjinakkan Three Thousand Burning Flame.

260
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:22,440
Tapi tenang saja.

261
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:23,920
Tingkat segel naga itu,

262
00:17:23,930 --> 00:17:26,920
jauh lebih tinggi dari yang dimiliki Three Thousand Burning Flame.

263
00:17:27,210 --> 00:17:28,440
Jika caramu tepat,

264
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,160
aku yakin kau bisa menjinakkannya.

265
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:32,240
Baiklah.

266
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:33,160
Aku percaya padamu.

267
00:17:33,970 --> 00:17:35,360
Kalau ada sedikit kesempatan,

268
00:17:35,370 --> 00:17:36,400
aku juga ingin mencoba.

269
00:17:37,490 --> 00:17:38,360
Tenang saja,

270
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:39,400
aku tahu batasanku.

271
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,530
Karena sudah datang jauh-jauh ke Zhongzhou,

272
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,710
maka tidak boleh pulang dengan tangan kosong.
